{
  "video_id": "YsA_JTeHJ6A",
  "title": "How to design a library that makes kids want to read |  Michael Bierut",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12740.0,
      "end_time": 17196.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s this thing called the law of unintended consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17220.0,
      "end_time": 18956.0,
      "text": "I thought it was just like a saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18980.0,
      "end_time": 20556.0,
      "text": "but it actually exists, I guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20580.0,
      "end_time": 22500.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s, like, academic papers about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22940.0,
      "end_time": 24196.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m a designer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24220.0,
      "end_time": 27760.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t like unintended consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27100.0,
      "end_time": 31676.0,
      "text": "People hire me because they have consequences that they really intend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31700.0,
      "end_time": 35556.0,
      "text": "and what they intend is for me to help them achieve those consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35580.0,
      "end_time": 38596.0,
      "text": "So I live in fear of unintended consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38620.0,
      "end_time": 43300.0,
      "text": "And so this is a story about consequences intended and unintended."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43900.0,
      "end_time": 47360.0,
      "text": "I got called by an organization called Robin Hood"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47600.0,
      "end_time": 48636.0,
      "text": "to do a favor for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48660.0,
      "end_time": 52750.0,
      "text": "Robin Hood is based in New York, a wonderful philanthropic organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52100.0,
      "end_time": 53836.0,
      "text": "that does what it says in the name."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53860.0,
      "end_time": 56635.0,
      "text": "They take from rich people, give it to poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56660.0,
      "end_time": 61556.0,
      "text": "In this case, what they wanted to benefit was the New York City school system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61580.0,
      "end_time": 66916.0,
      "text": "a huge enterprise that educates more than a million students at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66940.0,
      "end_time": 69276.0,
      "text": "and in buildings that are like this one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69300.0,
      "end_time": 71196.0,
      "text": "old buildings, big buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71220.0,
      "end_time": 74356.0,
      "text": "drafty buildings, sometimes buildings that are in disrepair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74380.0,
      "end_time": 76916.0,
      "text": "certainly buildings that could use a renovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76940.0,
      "end_time": 80196.0,
      "text": "Robin Hood had this ambition to improve these buildings in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80220.0,
      "end_time": 81676.0,
      "text": "but what they realized was"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81700.0,
      "end_time": 86236.0,
      "text": "to fix the buildings would be too expensive and impractical."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 90636.0,
      "text": "So instead they tried to figure out what one room they could go into"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90660.0,
      "end_time": 93716.0,
      "text": "in each of these buildings, in as many buildings that they could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93740.0,
      "end_time": 96396.0,
      "text": "and fix that one room"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96420.0,
      "end_time": 99236.0,
      "text": "so that they could improve the lives of the children inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 100476.0,
      "text": "as they were studying."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100500.0,
      "end_time": 102916.0,
      "text": "And what they came up with was the school library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102940.0,
      "end_time": 105876.0,
      "text": "and they came up with this idea called the Library Initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105900.0,
      "end_time": 108276.0,
      "text": "All the students have to pass through the library."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108300.0,
      "end_time": 109636.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where the books are."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109660.0,
      "end_time": 111996.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where the heart and soul of the school is."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112200.0,
      "end_time": 113436.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s fix these libraries."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113460.0,
      "end_time": 115996.0,
      "text": "So they did this wonderful thing where they brought in"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116200.0,
      "end_time": 119116.0,
      "text": "first 10, then 20, then more architects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119140.0,
      "end_time": 122876.0,
      "text": "each one of whom was assigned a library to rethink what a library was."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122900.0,
      "end_time": 124956.0,
      "text": "They trained special librarians."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124980.0,
      "end_time": 127360.0,
      "text": "So they started this mighty enterprise"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 130760.0,
      "text": "to reform public schools by improving these libraries."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130100.0,
      "end_time": 133756.0,
      "text": "Then they called me up and they said, \"Could you make a little contribution?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133780.0,
      "end_time": 135796.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Sure, what do you want me to do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135820.0,
      "end_time": 138676.0,
      "text": "And they said, \"Well, we want you to be the graphic designer"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138700.0,
      "end_time": 140155.0,
      "text": "in charge of the whole thing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140180.0,
      "end_time": 143756.0,
      "text": "And so I thought, I know what that means. That means I get to design a logo."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143780.0,
      "end_time": 145796.0,
      "text": "I know how to design that. I design logos."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145820.0,
      "end_time": 147476.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what people come to me for."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147500.0,
      "end_time": 149596.0,
      "text": "So OK, let&#39;s design a logo for this thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149620.0,
      "end_time": 151876.0,
      "text": "Easy to do, actually, compared with architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151900.0,
      "end_time": 153156.0,
      "text": "and being a librarian."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153180.0,
      "end_time": 155916.0,
      "text": "Just do a logo, make a contribution, and then you&#39;re out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155940.0,
      "end_time": 157876.0,
      "text": "and you feel really good about yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157900.0,
      "end_time": 161676.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m a great guy and I like to feel good about myself when I do these favors."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161700.0,
      "end_time": 163275.0,
      "text": "So I thought, let&#39;s overdeliver."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163300.0,
      "end_time": 166236.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to give you three logos, all based on this one idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168596.0,
      "text": "So you have three options, pick any of the three."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168620.0,
      "end_time": 169916.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all great, I said."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169940.0,
      "end_time": 173156.0,
      "text": "So the basic idea was these would be new school libraries"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 173180.0,
      "end_time": 174716.0,
      "text": "for New York schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 174740.0,
      "end_time": 178596.0,
      "text": "and so the idea is that it&#39;s a new thing, a new idea that needs a new name."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178620.0,
      "end_time": 183636.0,
      "text": "What I wanted to do was dispel the idea that these were musty old libraries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183660.0,
      "end_time": 187276.0,
      "text": "the kind of places that everyone is bored with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 187300.0,
      "end_time": 189276.0,
      "text": "you know, not your grandparents&#39; library."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189300.0,
      "end_time": 190756.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t worry about that at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190780.0,
      "end_time": 192796.0,
      "text": "This is going to this new, exciting thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 192820.0,
      "end_time": 194760.0,
      "text": "not a boring library."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194100.0,
      "end_time": 195756.0,
      "text": "So option number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 195780.0,
      "end_time": 197796.0,
      "text": "so instead of thinking of it as a library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197820.0,
      "end_time": 201995.0,
      "text": "think of it as a place where it is like: do talk, do make loud noises."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202200.0,
      "end_time": 206360.0,
      "text": "Right? So no shushing, it&#39;s like a shush-free zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 206600.0,
      "end_time": 208236.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to call it the Reading Room."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 211636.0,
      "text": "That was option number one. OK, option number two."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211660.0,
      "end_time": 215760.0,
      "text": "Option number two was, wait for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 215100.0,
      "end_time": 216356.0,
      "text": "OWL."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 216380.0,
      "end_time": 217716.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll meet you at OWL."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217740.0,
      "end_time": 221360.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m getting my book from the OWL. Meet you after school down at OWL."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221600.0,
      "end_time": 223396.0,
      "text": "I like that, right? Now, what does OWL stand for?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223420.0,
      "end_time": 225315.0,
      "text": "Well, it could be One World Library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225340.0,
      "end_time": 227956.0,
      "text": "or it could be Open. Wonder. Learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227980.0,
      "end_time": 232476.0,
      "text": "Or it could be -- and I figure librarians could figure out other things it could be"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232500.0,
      "end_time": 233956.0,
      "text": "because they know about words."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233980.0,
      "end_time": 235196.0,
      "text": "So other things, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235220.0,
      "end_time": 237676.0,
      "text": "And then look at this. It&#39;s like the eye of the owl."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237700.0,
      "end_time": 239396.0,
      "text": "This is irresistible in my opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239420.0,
      "end_time": 240875.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s even another idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 240900.0,
      "end_time": 242116.0,
      "text": "Option number three."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 242140.0,
      "end_time": 244756.0,
      "text": "Option number three was based actually on language."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 244780.0,
      "end_time": 248760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the idea that \"read\" is the past tense of \"read,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 248100.0,
      "end_time": 249956.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re both spelled the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249980.0,
      "end_time": 252916.0,
      "text": "So why don&#39;t we call this place The Red Zone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 252940.0,
      "end_time": 254369.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll meet you at the Red Zone."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 254393.0,
      "end_time": 256952.0,
      "text": "Are you Red? Get Red."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 257700.0,
      "end_time": 258916.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m well Red."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 258940.0,
      "end_time": 260156.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 260180.0,
      "end_time": 261516.0,
      "text": "I really loved this idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 261540.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263876.0,
      "text": "and I somehow was not focused on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 263900.0,
      "end_time": 269796.0,
      "text": "that librarians as a class are sort of interested in spelling and I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 269820.0,
      "end_time": 271755.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 271779.0,
      "end_time": 275276.0,
      "text": "But sometimes cleverness is more important than spelling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 275300.0,
      "end_time": 277716.0,
      "text": "and I thought this would be one of those instances."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277740.0,
      "end_time": 279756.0,
      "text": "So usually when I make these presentations"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279780.0,
      "end_time": 282556.0,
      "text": "I say there&#39;s just one question and the question should be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 282580.0,
      "end_time": 283955.0,
      "text": "\"How can I thank you, Mike?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 283980.0,
      "end_time": 286596.0,
      "text": "But in this case, the question was more like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 286620.0,
      "end_time": 289360.0,
      "text": "\"Um, are you kidding?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 289600.0,
      "end_time": 290756.0,
      "text": "Because, they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 290780.0,
      "end_time": 292155.0,
      "text": "the premise of all this work"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 292180.0,
      "end_time": 296316.0,
      "text": "was that kids were bored with old libraries, musty old libraries."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 296340.0,
      "end_time": 297556.0,
      "text": "They were tired of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 297580.0,
      "end_time": 300916.0,
      "text": "And instead, they said, these kids have never really seen a library."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 300940.0,
      "end_time": 302756.0,
      "text": "The school libraries in these schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 302780.0,
      "end_time": 306195.0,
      "text": "are really so dilapidated, if they&#39;re there at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 306220.0,
      "end_time": 308156.0,
      "text": "that they haven&#39;t bored anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 308180.0,
      "end_time": 311156.0,
      "text": "They haven&#39;t even been there to bore anyone at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 311180.0,
      "end_time": 314596.0,
      "text": "So the idea was, just forget about giving it a new name."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 314620.0,
      "end_time": 318676.0,
      "text": "Just call it, one last try, a library."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 318700.0,
      "end_time": 319916.0,
      "text": "Right? OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 319940.0,
      "end_time": 322796.0,
      "text": "So I thought, OK, give it a little oomph?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 322820.0,
      "end_time": 324360.0,
      "text": "Exclamation point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 324600.0,
      "end_time": 326360.0,
      "text": "Then -- this is because I&#39;m clever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 326600.0,
      "end_time": 328596.0,
      "text": "move that into the \"i,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 328620.0,
      "end_time": 329876.0,
      "text": "make it red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 329900.0,
      "end_time": 332750.0,
      "text": "and there you have it, the Library Initiative."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 332100.0,
      "end_time": 334636.0,
      "text": "So I thought, mission accomplished, there&#39;s your logo."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 334660.0,
      "end_time": 337716.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s interesting about this logo, an unintended consequence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 337740.0,
      "end_time": 340876.0,
      "text": "was that it turned out that they didn&#39;t really even need my design"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 340900.0,
      "end_time": 343876.0,
      "text": "because you could type it any font, you could write it by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343900.0,
      "end_time": 345996.0,
      "text": "and when they started sending emails around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 346200.0,
      "end_time": 347596.0,
      "text": "they just would use Shift and 1,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 347620.0,
      "end_time": 350196.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d get their own logo just right out of the thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 350220.0,
      "end_time": 351956.0,
      "text": "And I thought, well, that&#39;s fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 351980.0,
      "end_time": 353756.0,
      "text": "Feel free to use that logo."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 353780.0,
      "end_time": 356676.0,
      "text": "And then I embarked on the real rollout of this thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 356700.0,
      "end_time": 358635.0,
      "text": "working with every one of the architects"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 358660.0,
      "end_time": 361660.0,
      "text": "to put this logo on the front door of their own library. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 362180.0,
      "end_time": 363556.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the big rollout."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 363580.0,
      "end_time": 365835.0,
      "text": "Basically I&#39;d work with different architects."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 365860.0,
      "end_time": 369760.0,
      "text": "First Robin Hood was my client. Now these architects were my client."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 369100.0,
      "end_time": 371339.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d say, \"Here&#39;s your logo. Put it on the door.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 371363.0,
      "end_time": 373316.0,
      "text": "\"Here&#39;s your logo. Put it on both doors.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 373340.0,
      "end_time": 375356.0,
      "text": "\"Here&#39;s your logo. Put it off to the side.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 375380.0,
      "end_time": 377635.0,
      "text": "\"Here&#39;s your logo repeated all over to the top.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 377660.0,
      "end_time": 379356.0,
      "text": "So everything was going swimmingly."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 379380.0,
      "end_time": 382360.0,
      "text": "I just was saying, \"Here&#39;s your logo. Here&#39;s your logo.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 382600.0,
      "end_time": 384196.0,
      "text": "Then I got a call from one of the architects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 384220.0,
      "end_time": 387760.0,
      "text": "a guy named Richard Lewis, and he says, \"I&#39;ve got a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 387100.0,
      "end_time": 389116.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re the graphics guy. Can you solve it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 389140.0,
      "end_time": 390356.0,
      "text": "And I said, OK, sure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 390380.0,
      "end_time": 392956.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"The problem is that there&#39;s a space"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 392980.0,
      "end_time": 394796.0,
      "text": "between the shelf and the ceiling.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 394820.0,
      "end_time": 397156.0,
      "text": "So that sounds like an architectural issue to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 397180.0,
      "end_time": 399276.0,
      "text": "not a graphic design issue, so I&#39;m, \"Go on.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 399300.0,
      "end_time": 402956.0,
      "text": "And Richard says, \"Well, the top shelf has to be low enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 402980.0,
      "end_time": 404196.0,
      "text": "for the kid to reach it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 404220.0,
      "end_time": 407220.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m in a big old building, and the ceilings are really high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 407244.0,
      "end_time": 409316.0,
      "text": "so actually I&#39;ve got all this space up there"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 409340.0,
      "end_time": 411360.0,
      "text": "and I need something like a mural.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 411600.0,
      "end_time": 413996.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m like, \"Whoa, you know, I&#39;m a logo designer."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 414200.0,
      "end_time": 416156.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not Diego Rivera or something."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 416180.0,
      "end_time": 417796.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not a muralist.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 417820.0,
      "end_time": 420195.0,
      "text": "And so he said, \"But can&#39;t you think of anything?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 420220.0,
      "end_time": 425596.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"OK, what if we just took pictures of the kids in the school"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 425620.0,
      "end_time": 428760.0,
      "text": "and just put them around the top of the thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 428100.0,
      "end_time": 429436.0,
      "text": "and maybe that could work.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 429460.0,
      "end_time": 431316.0,
      "text": "And my wife is a photographer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 431340.0,
      "end_time": 433275.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Dorothy, there&#39;s no budget,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 433300.0,
      "end_time": 436476.0,
      "text": "can you come to this school in east New York, take these pictures?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 436500.0,
      "end_time": 437716.0,
      "text": "And she did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 437740.0,
      "end_time": 439716.0,
      "text": "and if you go in Richard&#39;s library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 439740.0,
      "end_time": 441596.0,
      "text": "which is one of the first that opened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 441620.0,
      "end_time": 444716.0,
      "text": "it has this glorious frieze of, like, the heroes of the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 444740.0,
      "end_time": 446436.0,
      "text": "oversized, looking down"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 446460.0,
      "end_time": 449476.0,
      "text": "into the little dollhouse of the real library, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 449500.0,
      "end_time": 452316.0,
      "text": "And the kids were great, hand-selected by the principals"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 452340.0,
      "end_time": 454116.0,
      "text": "and the librarian."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 454140.0,
      "end_time": 457395.0,
      "text": "It just kind of created this heroic atmosphere in this library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 457420.0,
      "end_time": 460916.0,
      "text": "this very dignified setting below and the joy of the children above."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 460940.0,
      "end_time": 465276.0,
      "text": "So naturally all the other librarians in the other schools see this"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 465300.0,
      "end_time": 467236.0,
      "text": "and they said, well, we want murals too."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 468556.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m like, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 468580.0,
      "end_time": 471476.0,
      "text": "So then I think, well, it can&#39;t be the same mural every time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 471500.0,
      "end_time": 474556.0,
      "text": "so Dorothy did another one, and then she did another one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 474580.0,
      "end_time": 476195.0,
      "text": "but then we needed more help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 476220.0,
      "end_time": 479760.0,
      "text": "so I called an illustrator I knew named Lynn Pauley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 479100.0,
      "end_time": 482360.0,
      "text": "and Lynn did these beautiful paintings of the kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 482600.0,
      "end_time": 486396.0,
      "text": "Then I called a guy named Charles Wilkin at a place called Automatic Design."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 486420.0,
      "end_time": 488220.0,
      "text": "He did these amazing collages."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 488780.0,
      "end_time": 491116.0,
      "text": "We had Rafael Esquer"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 491140.0,
      "end_time": 492996.0,
      "text": "do these great silhouettes."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 493200.0,
      "end_time": 495195.0,
      "text": "He would work with the kids, asking for words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 495220.0,
      "end_time": 496796.0,
      "text": "and then based on those prompts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 496820.0,
      "end_time": 499516.0,
      "text": "come up with this little, delirious kind of constellation"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 499540.0,
      "end_time": 501596.0,
      "text": "of silhouettes of things that are in books."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 501620.0,
      "end_time": 503196.0,
      "text": "Peter Arkle interviewed the kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 503220.0,
      "end_time": 505316.0,
      "text": "and had them talk about their favorite books"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 505340.0,
      "end_time": 507595.0,
      "text": "and he put their testimony as a frieze up there."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 507620.0,
      "end_time": 509876.0,
      "text": "Stefan Sagmeister worked with Yuko Shimizu"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 509900.0,
      "end_time": 512196.0,
      "text": "and they did this amazing manga-style statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 512220.0,
      "end_time": 514676.0,
      "text": "\"Everyone who is honest is interesting,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 514700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516556.00000000006,
      "text": "that goes all the way around."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 516580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518956.00000000006,
      "text": "Christoph Niemann, brilliant illustrator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 518980.0,
      "end_time": 520356.0,
      "text": "did a whole series of things"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 520380.0,
      "end_time": 523395.0,
      "text": "where he embedded books into the faces and characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 523419.0,
      "end_time": 526555.0,
      "text": "and images and places that you find in the books."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 526580.0,
      "end_time": 528619.0,
      "text": "And then even Maira Kalman"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 528660.0,
      "end_time": 532475.0,
      "text": "did this amazing cryptic installation of objects and words"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 532499.0,
      "end_time": 535676.0,
      "text": "that kind of go all around and will fascinate students"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 535700.0,
      "end_time": 537276.0,
      "text": "for as long as it&#39;s up there."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 537300.0,
      "end_time": 538955.0,
      "text": "So this was really satisfying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 538980.0,
      "end_time": 544876.0,
      "text": "and basically my role here was reading a series of dimensions to these artists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 544900.0,
      "end_time": 546156.0,
      "text": "and I would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 546180.0,
      "end_time": 548876.0,
      "text": "\"Three feet by 15 feet, whatever you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 548900.0,
      "end_time": 551116.0,
      "text": "Let me know if you have any problem with that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 551140.0,
      "end_time": 554356.0,
      "text": "And they would go and install these. It just was the greatest thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 554380.0,
      "end_time": 556676.0,
      "text": "But the greatest thing, actually, was --"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 556700.0,
      "end_time": 557916.0,
      "text": "Every once in a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 557940.0,
      "end_time": 561156.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d get, like, an invitation in the mail made of construction paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 561180.0,
      "end_time": 564476.0,
      "text": "and it would say, \"You are invited to the opening of our new library.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 564500.0,
      "end_time": 566876.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;d go to the library, say, you&#39;d go to PS10,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 566900.0,
      "end_time": 568116.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;d go inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 568140.0,
      "end_time": 570915.0,
      "text": "There&#39;d be balloons, there&#39;d be a student ambassador,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 570940.0,
      "end_time": 573760.0,
      "text": "there&#39;d be speeches that were read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 573100.0,
      "end_time": 575996.0,
      "text": "poetry that was written specifically for the opening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 576200.0,
      "end_time": 578956.0,
      "text": "dignitaries would present people with certificates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 578980.0,
      "end_time": 581596.0,
      "text": "and the whole thing was just a delirious, fun party."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 581620.0,
      "end_time": 583236.0,
      "text": "So I loved going to these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 586236.0,
      "text": "I would stand there dressed like this, obviously not belonging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 586260.0,
      "end_time": 588927.0,
      "text": "and someone would say, \"What are you doing here, mister?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 588951.0,
      "end_time": 592116.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d say, \"Well, I&#39;m part of the team that designed this place.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 592140.0,
      "end_time": 594450.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;d said, \"You do these shelves?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 594690.0,
      "end_time": 596476.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"No.\" \"You took the pictures up above.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 596500.0,
      "end_time": 597716.0,
      "text": "\"No.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 597740.0,
      "end_time": 598956.0,
      "text": "\"Well, what did you do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 598980.0,
      "end_time": 601436.0,
      "text": "\"You know when you came in? The sign over the door?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 601460.0,
      "end_time": 602876.0,
      "text": "\"The sign that says library?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 602900.0,
      "end_time": 603915.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 603940.0,
      "end_time": 605156.0,
      "text": "\"Yeah, I did that!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 605180.0,
      "end_time": 609300.0,
      "text": "And then they&#39;d sort of go, \"OK. Nice work if you can get it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 610200.0,
      "end_time": 614116.0,
      "text": "So it was so satisfying going to these little openings"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 614140.0,
      "end_time": 617876.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that I was kind of largely ignored or humiliated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 617900.0,
      "end_time": 620760.0,
      "text": "but it was actually fun going to the openings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 620100.0,
      "end_time": 622796.0,
      "text": "so I decided that I wanted to get the people in my office"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 622820.0,
      "end_time": 626276.0,
      "text": "who had worked on these projects, get the illustrators and photographers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 626300.0,
      "end_time": 627996.0,
      "text": "and I said, why don&#39;t we rent a van"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 628200.0,
      "end_time": 630396.0,
      "text": "and drive around the five boroughs of New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 630420.0,
      "end_time": 632435.0,
      "text": "and see how many we could hit at one time."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 632460.0,
      "end_time": 635316.0,
      "text": "And eventually there were going to be 60 of these libraries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 635340.0,
      "end_time": 639116.0,
      "text": "so we probably got to see maybe half a dozen in one long day."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 639140.0,
      "end_time": 642760.0,
      "text": "And the best thing of all was meeting these librarians"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 642100.0,
      "end_time": 645676.0,
      "text": "who kind of were running these, took possession of these places"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 645700.0,
      "end_time": 648276.0,
      "text": "like their private stage upon which they were invited"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 648300.0,
      "end_time": 652236.0,
      "text": "to mesmerize their students and bring the books to life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 654795.0,
      "text": "and it was just this really exciting experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 654820.0,
      "end_time": 657636.0,
      "text": "for all of us to actually see these things in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 657660.0,
      "end_time": 660195.0,
      "text": "So we spent a long day doing this"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 660220.0,
      "end_time": 662360.0,
      "text": "and we were in the very last library."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 664876.0,
      "text": "It was still winter, because it got dark early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 664900.0,
      "end_time": 666116.0,
      "text": "and the librarian says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 666140.0,
      "end_time": 668836.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m about to close down. So really nice having you here."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 668860.0,
      "end_time": 671996.0,
      "text": "Hey, wait a second, do you want to see how I turn off the lights?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 672200.0,
      "end_time": 673316.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m like, \"OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 673340.0,
      "end_time": 675836.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"I have this special way that I do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 675860.0,
      "end_time": 677116.0,
      "text": "And then she showed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 677140.0,
      "end_time": 680596.0,
      "text": "What she did was she turned out every light one by one by one by one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 680620.0,
      "end_time": 682676.0,
      "text": "and the last light she left on"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 682700.0,
      "end_time": 685596.0,
      "text": "was the light that illuminated the kids&#39; faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 685620.0,
      "end_time": 688476.0,
      "text": "and she said, \"That&#39;s the last light I turn off every night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 688500.0,
      "end_time": 691760.0,
      "text": "because I like to remind myself why I come to work.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 691100.0,
      "end_time": 693956.0,
      "text": "So when I started this whole thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 693980.0,
      "end_time": 696171.0,
      "text": "remember, it was just about designing that logo"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 696195.0,
      "end_time": 698196.0,
      "text": "and being clever, come up with a new name?"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 698220.0,
      "end_time": 699796.0,
      "text": "The unintended consequence here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 699820.0,
      "end_time": 701636.0,
      "text": "which I would like to take credit for"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 701660.0,
      "end_time": 704876.0,
      "text": "and like to think I can think through the experience to that extent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 704900.0,
      "end_time": 706116.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 706140.0,
      "end_time": 710116.0,
      "text": "I was just focused on a foot ahead of me, as far as I could reach with my own hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 710140.0,
      "end_time": 712716.0,
      "text": "Instead, way off in the distance"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 712740.0,
      "end_time": 713996.0,
      "text": "was a librarian"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 714200.0,
      "end_time": 716956.0,
      "text": "who was going to find the chain of consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 716980.0,
      "end_time": 718396.0,
      "text": "that we had set in motion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 718420.0,
      "end_time": 719915.0,
      "text": "a source of inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 719940.0,
      "end_time": 723316.0,
      "text": "so that she in this case could do her work really well."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 723340.0,
      "end_time": 726716.0,
      "text": "40,000 kids a year are affected by these libraries."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 726740.0,
      "end_time": 729196.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been happening for more than 10 years now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 729220.0,
      "end_time": 733756.0,
      "text": "so those librarians have kind of turned on a generation of children to books"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 733780.0,
      "end_time": 736276.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s been a thrill to find out"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 736300.0,
      "end_time": 740360.0,
      "text": "that sometimes unintended consequences are the best consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 740600.0,
      "end_time": 741276.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 741300.0,
      "end_time": 745180.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}